{"tid":2007864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"now政情內會今日回顧及最新分析","createTime":"2020-05-08T14:58:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T22:40:41.000Z","uid":164435,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e2b2bb06d908ece4418127c59b1d64db0407dcc4","tid":2007864,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:58:34.000Z","msg":"可直接到now新聞App或 <a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=390372\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D390372&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQPhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=95d3d5a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D390372&h=7a732b55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=390372</a> 查看新聞內容<br />\nFacebook︰<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/263143884538149/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F263143884538149%2F&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQPhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=7ba78400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/263143884538149/</a><br />\nInstagram︰<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/nownews_politics\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fnownews_politics&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQPhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=421252c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.instagram.com/nownews_politics</a><br />\n<br />\n【政情】建制佈局葉劉為李慧琼助攻 泛民批保安為建制「加持」<br />\n【Now新聞台】立法會內務委員會主持鬧雙胞，透過動作片打破半年多的僵局。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>內會原定兩點半開始，但戰線提前早一小時，戰場放在與內會同一地點舉行的教育事務委員會。據聞，泛民也齊集伺機搶位，但主席葉劉淑儀延長會議，待建制派齊集議事廳，具有先天優勢的葉太一宣布休會，就將座位與李慧琼無縫交接。</strong></span>據聞，建制派吸納了逃犯修例法案委員會的教訓，明白要佔上風金就要搶到主席位。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>多名民主派向《政情》指，他們錯失了最佳搶位時機，因為立法會保安加持建制派，除了保安主動護送李慧琼，他們的行動亦受保安阻撓，加上李慧琼相對年輕，又是女議員，令男議員行動多了顧忌。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n秘書處亦守嚴守採訪安排，禁止記者進入會議室採訪，令逃犯修例時會議室混亂場面，不再出現。<br />\n<br />\n建制派一早預計動作片，據聞亦按排了「勇武」角色周浩鼎、何俊賢壯丁，與保安包圍主席台防突襲，郭偉强更與陳志全拉扯。《政情》聽聞，60歲以上的建制派獲豁免衝撞場面，至於何解70歲黃定光同樣留守前線。有建制笑言：「他以為自己25歲。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>李慧琼在會上幾乎趕走一半的民主派議員後，順利完成所有議程後散會。有建制派認為，今次打破內會僵局後，日後能否選出主席已經不重要，反正李慧琼是否當選，都收取較普通議員高一截的內會主席月薪。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"04ea0a82d9a5c5493a17d38ea9b37f5f887c39cc","tid":2007864,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T15:01:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8dabf87b7bafe348d5af326514ef5ad1033520cc","tid":2007864,"uid":59818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T15:04:06.000Z","msg":"泛民一早搶到其實都會比保安抬走"},{"pid":"a4dea7c2e30d390949ea7a4aafc79969ed0153d7","tid":2007864,"uid":14494,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T15:04:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">今次打破內會僵局後，日後能否選出主席已經不重要，反正李慧琼是否當選</span><br />\n講真話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁仲選主席黎做乜"},{"pid":"0294a7a1cd8b4d73b6c1db5dcae4442ad92cde96","tid":2007864,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T15:04:48.000Z","msg":"最尾唔係幾明"},{"pid":"923f407787468cc35c871690f84f928a138074c3","tid":2007864,"uid":92448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T15:06:30.000Z","msg":"建制笑言<br />\n曱甴好撚好笑?"},{"pid":"4f4947ee8212a0bba96a81b4ac0345cb0f34c2cb","tid":2007864,"uid":164435,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4dea7c2e30d390949ea7a4aafc79969ed0153d7","tid":2007864,"uid":14494,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T15:04:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">今次打破內會僵局後，日後能否選出主席已經不重要，反正李慧琼是否當選</span><br />\n講真話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁仲選主席黎做乜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T15:12:06.000Z","msg":"應該大家都係見步行步<br />\n反正再選唔到主席<br />\n保皇黨就會話啲嘢係急切又搵李慧琼返嚟開"},{"pid":"845bcfba3e965ea84b9ad522066289aca0936c9f","tid":2007864,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4f4947ee8212a0bba96a81b4ac034